name: Feline Frenzy (4skins)
description:
Play  minigames as a cat! Minigames represent your everyday struggles as a cat... 

There are 13 total minigames, each more unique than the last. All games are played using only the Left Mouse Button (LMB). Try completing as many minigames as you can!
